            </p>
          </dt>
          <dd
            class="order-first text-5xl font-normal font-mono text-accent-600">
            30%
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col bg-base-50 p-8 rounded-3xl">
          <dt class="mt-4">
            <p class="tracking-tight text-lg font-medium text-base-900">
              Super low fee
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-base-500 text-pretty mt-2">
              Enjoy significant savings with our extremely low fee structure.
            </p>
          </dt>
          <dd
            class="order-first text-5xl font-normal font-mono text-accent-600">
            40%
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col bg-base-50 p-8 rounded-3xl">
          <dt class="mt-4">
            <p class="tracking-tight text-lg font-medium text-base-900">
              Massive Earnings
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-base-500 text-pretty mt-2">
              Reap the benefits with substantial returns.
            </p>
          </dt>
          <dd
            class="order-first text-5xl font-normal font-mono text-accent-600">
            50%
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col bg-base-50 p-8 rounded-3xl">
          <dt class="mt-4">
            <p class="tracking-tight text-lg font-medium text-base-900">
              Growing Impact
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-base-500 text-pretty mt-2">
              Join 60 million satisfied users who trust our services.
            </p>
          </dt>
          <dd
            class="order-first text-5xl font-normal font-mono text-accent-600">
            60M
          </dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
